cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use JarvisVR in your research or projects, please cite it."
title: "JarvisVR — an AI agentic operating system for mixed reality on the Meta Quest 3"
abstract: >-
  JarvisVR is an open-source AI agentic operating system for mixed reality on the
  Meta Quest 3. A planning LLM agent perceives the user's real environment
  (color passthrough vision, ambient audio, and gaze), calls tools, and renders
  interactive 3D holographic widgets the user manipulates with their hands, all
  over a single versioned WebSocket protocol.
type: software
authors:
  - name: "The JarvisVR contributors"
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-06-08"
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/sumitaich1998/jarvisvr"
url: "https://github.com/sumitaich1998/jarvisvr"
keywords:
